---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Press Kit" description="Press resources for Parting Shadows by Wunderelf Studios. Logos, screenshots, and fact sheet.">
  <section class="py-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Press Kit</h1>
        <div class="w-16 h-1 bg-teal mx-auto rounded-full" />
        <p class="text-text-muted mt-6 max-w-xl mx-auto">
          Resources for press, content creators, and media coverage.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Fact Sheet -->
      <div class="bg-dark-card border border-dark-border rounded-xl p-8 mb-12">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-gold">Fact Sheet</h2>
        <dl class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-x-8 gap-y-4">
          <div>
            <dt class="text-sm text-text-muted uppercase tracking-wider font-heading">Developer</dt>
            <dd class="text-text font-medium mt-1">Wunderelf Studios</dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt class="text-sm text-text-muted uppercase tracking-wider font-heading">Title</dt>
            <dd class="text-text font-medium mt-1">Parting Shadows</dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt class="text-sm text-text-muted uppercase tracking-wider font-heading">Genre</dt>
            <dd class="text-text font-medium mt-1">Narrative RPG / Turn-Based</dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt class="text-sm text-text-muted uppercase tracking-wider font-heading">Platform</dt>
            <dd class="text-text font-medium mt-1">PC, Mac, Linux (Steam)</dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt class="text-sm text-text-muted uppercase tracking-wider font-heading">Players</dt>
            <dd class="text-text font-medium mt-1">1-3 (local & online co-op)</dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt class="text-sm text-text-muted uppercase tracking-wider font-heading">Engine</dt>
            <dd class="text-text font-medium mt-1">Godot 4</dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt class="text-sm text-text-muted uppercase tracking-wider font-heading">Status</dt>
            <dd class="text-text font-medium mt-1">Available Now</dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt class="text-sm text-text-muted uppercase tracking-wider font-heading">Release</dt>
            <dd class="text-text font-medium mt-1">April 23, 2026</dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
      </div>

      <!-- Trailer -->
      <div class="bg-dark-card border border-dark-border rounded-xl p-8 mb-12">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-gold">Trailer</h2>
        <div class="aspect-video rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
          <iframe
            class="w-full h-full"
            src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/MBQrINcXLOI"
            title="Parting Shadows Official Trailer"
            frameborder="0"
            allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
            allowfullscreen
          ></iframe>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Description -->
      <div class="bg-dark-card border border-dark-border rounded-xl p-8 mb-12">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-gold">Description</h2>

        <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold text-text mb-2">Short</h3>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Parting Shadows is a narrative RPG with 56 classes, branching stories, and co-op multiplayer.
          Every choice shapes the world.
        </p>

        <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold text-text mb-2">Long</h3>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
          Parting Shadows is a turn-based narrative RPG where every decision shapes the story.
          Build a party of three from 6 base classes -- Squire, Mage, Entertainer, Tinker,
          Wildling, and Wanderer -- each branching into two tiers of specialization for 56
          unique classes. Train your Mage as an Invoker to unleash elemental devastation as an
          Infernalist, Tidecaller, or Tempest -- or walk the Acolyte's path toward Paladin,
          Priest, or Warlock. Battle through three interconnected story campaigns with branching
          paths, unique enemies, and multiple endings. Play solo or bring friends along with
          local and online co-op for up to 3 players, where the party votes on story branches
          together. Featuring speed-based turn order combat, 140+ abilities, and accessibility features including
          color blind modes and screen reader support.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Downloads -->
      <div class="bg-dark-card border border-dark-border rounded-xl p-8">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-gold">Downloads</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <a
            href="/press/logos.zip"
            class="flex items-center gap-3 p-4 bg-dark-surface border border-dark-border rounded-lg hover:border-teal/50 transition-colors"
          >
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-teal-light shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 10v6m0 0l-3-3m3 3l3-3m2 8H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
            </svg>
            <div>
              <div class="text-text font-medium">Logos</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-text-muted">Studio & game logos (PNG, SVG)</div>
            </div>
          </a>
          <a
            href="/press/screenshots.zip"
            class="flex items-center gap-3 p-4 bg-dark-surface border border-dark-border rounded-lg hover:border-teal/50 transition-colors"
          >
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-teal-light shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 10v6m0 0l-3-3m3 3l3-3m2 8H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
            </svg>
            <div>
              <div class="text-text font-medium">Screenshots</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-text-muted">Curated in-game screenshots</div>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-6">
          These assets are free to use for press coverage and content creation related to Parting Shadows.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Press Contact -->
      <div class="bg-dark-card border border-dark-border rounded-xl p-8 mt-12">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-gold">Press Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">
          For review keys, interview requests, or other press inquiries:
        </p>
        <a
          href="mailto:wunderelfstudios@gmail.com"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-teal-light hover:text-teal transition-colors font-medium"
        >
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
          </svg>
          wunderelfstudios@gmail.com
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
